      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so excited to share this absolute gem with you. This car is in incredible, showroom-quality condition\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s as close to new as you can get, you\u2019ve found it! Come take a look before someone else grabs it!",
