    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to achieve its 8,400 RPM redline with surgical throttle response. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, transmitting power through a perfectly calibrated M-Variable differential. This specimen is mechanically pristine, with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service already completed. The chassis remains taut, showing zero subframe fatigue, and the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) provides flawless damping across all modes. With original paint depth and a cabin devoid of bolster wear, this is a concours-level example for the collector demanding mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
