      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero paint chips or swirl marks. The interior is equally pristine; the premium leather remains supple and entirely free of creases or wear, still retaining its original factory scent. Every electronic component and interior feature operates with crisp, out-of-the-box precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Always garage-kept under a breathable cover and never driven in inclement weather, this car is suited for the most demanding collector seeking a turn-key masterpiece. Includes all original manuals, keys, and a comprehensive service binder.",
