      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem! It has been my pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been kept in a garage, meticulously cared for, and is in truly flawless condition inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one! I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
