      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade BMW E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This example features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies, delivering a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including a documented VANOS rebuild, rod bearing replacement, and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains factory-correct with no bushing deflection, and the compression across all six cylinders is within 2% of factory spec. A truly turn-key, investment-quality machine for the technical purist.",
